snippet.title: Freedom Hill Community
snippet.description: Freedom Hill is a Messiah-centered community of believers and media-driven ministry based in St. Charles, MO. We are devoted to proclaiming the Gospel of Yeshua (Jesus) and pursuing the roots of our Christian faith. We follow the Scriptures and encourage individuals and families to live for Yeshua with a foundation of the Spirit and the Truth. Our focus as a local community is to live out God’s Word in love by coming together as mishpacha (family) in worship, study, discipleship, celebration, and sharing the Gospel.
